tuatua
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:one of two species of edible New Zealand bivalve,  Paphies subtriangulata  or <i> P. donacina </i>, similar to but smaller than the toheroa.
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
